        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Arcane DC 47: <em>freeze time</em> (1/day, the classic opener) · <em>maze</em> · <em>wall of force</em> (his battlefield architecture) · <em>chain lightning</em> @Damage[8d12[electricity]] · <em>invisibility (4th)</em> · <em>teleport</em>/<em>gate</em> (his exits). He spends his first stolen round walling the battlefield into a killing floor.</p>"
